This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as word-level quality estimation and machine translation. The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper's focus on integrating local and global contextual information could also place it in the sub-categories of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) which deal with similar tasks of feature extraction and context integration.
